# 📝 Notes for Your Notebook

## Day 69 – Using the BloodReport Model

### Topics Learned

* Importing a model into a screen.
* Displaying data from an object.
* Separating UI from data.
* Computing health status from model values.

### Key Lesson

> **The UI should display data from a model instead of storing data directly. This makes it easy to replace sample data with real OCR results later without redesigning the screen.**

