# 🚀 Day 70 Preview

Tomorrow we'll begin preparing for **real OCR integration**.

We'll create a service layer (`services/`) that will eventually:

1. Receive the uploaded PDF or image.
2. Extract text using OCR.
3. Convert the extracted text into a `BloodReport` object.

This is an important architectural step because it keeps OCR logic separate from your UI, making the app easier to maintain as it grows.
